            "description": "Ventas A Services Ecommerce is a freelance project that I developed for a client. It is a platform that allows the client to sell their products online, manage inventory and customers orders. The website have a shopping cart without payment option (client request). When a order is submited a message is sent to client Whatsapp number and continues the process manually. The platform is developed in NextJS. It also uses MongoDB as a database and Tailwind for the frontend style. ",
